        <!-- <span>Snap</span> -->
    </a>

</div>






    

<div class="content_blocks">




    
<style>

</style>


  <div id="content_block-227573" class="content_block paragraph image triple_gutter_right triple_gutter_left center_align">
  <div class="content_inner_wrapper">



      <div class="media_wrapper">
        
  






  <img
    src="https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_760,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg"
    srcset="https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_220,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 220w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_300,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 300w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_400,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 400w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_600,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 600w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_750,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 750w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_840,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 840w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_960,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 960w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_1260,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 1260w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_1800,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 1800w,https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/w_2400,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:best/GettyImages-1202001675_ht0xjb/photo-by-allen-berezovsky-getty-images.jpg 2400w,"
    sizes="60vw"
    alt="Beyoncé, Jay-Z, and more shortlisted for 2022 Oscar nominations"
  />






<span class="img_caption">

    <span class="caption">
      Photo by Allen Berezovsky/Getty Images.
    </span>

  <span class="credit">
      &nbsp;

    
  </span>

</span>





      </div>

  </div>
</div>










    
<style>

</style>


  <div id="content_block-227574" class="content_block paragraph text triple_gutter_right triple_gutter_left center_align">
  <div class="content_inner_wrapper">




      <div class="paragraph_wrapper center_align">






          <p>
            The Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences has <a target="_new" href="https://www.oscars.org/oscars/94th-oscars-shortlists">shared</a> 10 shortlists of potential nominees at the 94th Oscars ceremony, which will take place on Sunday, March 27, 2022. Today's announcement includes possible candidates in the categories of Documentary Feature, Music (Original Score), and Music (Original Song), among others.
          </p>

            <div class="" style="padding-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: left;">
  <div class="ad  paragraph_wrapper">
    <div style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 5px;">ADVERTISEMENT</div>
        
<div id='div-above-latest-ad' >






      <div id="above-the-fold-ad">
        <script type='text/javascript'>
         var ad_id = displayAdSlot('above-the-fold-ad', 'fader_v3_article_above_the_fold1_300x250', [300, 250], true);
        </script>
      </div>





</div>


  </div>
</div>










          <p>
            The Documentary Feature shortlist includes three music films: <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/questlove">Questlove</a>'s, Todd Haynes' <i>The Velvet Undeground</i>, and <i>Billy Eilish: The World's a Little Blurry</i>.
          </p>



              <div class="related_inline">


  <a data-ga-event-category="Recirculation" data-ga-event-label="Related Inline" data-ga-on="click" data-ga-event-action="click" class="thumb permalink" href="/2023/02/02/glorilla-lil-wayne-future-missy-elliott-grammys-hip-hop-50-anniversary">
  <img class=""
    src="https://thefader-res.cloudinary.com/private_images/c_limit,w_1024/c_crop,h_527,w_1011,x_6,y_27/w_300,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:eco/Collage_Maker-02-Feb-2023-01.17-PM_s9e1rd/Collage_Maker-02-Feb-2023-01.17-PM_s9e1rd.jpg"
    alt="Grammys tap GloRilla, Missy Elliott, Lil Wayne for hip-hop 50th anniversary performance"
    sizes="100px"
  />
  </a>

  <div class="card_headline">
    <h3>Read Next:
      <a data-ga-event-category="Recirculation" data-ga-event-label="Related Inline" data-ga-on="click" data-ga-event-action="click" class="permalink" href="/2023/02/02/glorilla-lil-wayne-future-missy-elliott-grammys-hip-hop-50-anniversary">
        Grammys tap GloRilla, Missy Elliott, Lil Wayne for hip-hop 50th anniversary performance
      </a>
    </h3>
  </div>

</div>










          <p>
            The Original Score list is full of familiar names, such as Hans Zimmer (<i>Dune</i>, <i>No Time to Die</i>), <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/nicholas-britell">Nicholas Britell</a> (<i>Don't Look Up</i>), <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/alexandre-desplat">Alexandre Desplat</a> (<i>The French Dispatch</i>), and <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/jonny-greenwood">Jonny Greenwood</a> (<i>The Power of the Dog</i> and <i>Spencer</i>). 
          </p>

            <div class="" style="padding-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: left;">
  <div class="ad  paragraph_wrapper">
    <div style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 5px;">ADVERTISEMENT</div>
        
<div id='div-above-latest-ad' >






      <div id="above-the-fold-ad">
        <script type='text/javascript'>
         var ad_id = displayAdSlot('above-the-fold-ad', 'fader_v3_article_above_the_fold2_300x250', [300, 250], true);
        </script>
      </div>





</div>


  </div>
</div>










          <p>
            The Original Song list is similarly star studded. <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/beyonce-1">Beyoncé</a>'s "<a href="https://www.thefader.com/2021/11/12/beyonce-be-alive-king-richard">Be Alive</a>." from the <i>King Richard</i> soundtrack appears alongside <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/jay-z">Jay-Z</a> and <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/kid-cudi">Kid Cudi</a>'s "<a href="https://www.thefader.com/2021/10/29/listen-to-2-new-jay-z-songs">Guns Go Bang</a>" from <i>The Harder They Fall</i>, and <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/ariana-grande">Ariana Grande</a> and Kid Cudi's "Just Look Up" from <i>Don't Look Up</i>. "Be Alive" would be Beyoncé's first Oscar nomination, though she's performed at the ceremony in previous years. If it's nominated along with "Guns Go Bang," 2022 will be the first time a married couple competes for an Oscar in any category. And if "Guns Go Bang" and "<a href="https://www.thefader.com/2021/12/03/ariana-grande-and-kid-cudi-just-look-up">Just Look Up</a>" both make the next cut, Kid Cudi will be the first artist to be up for two Best Original Song Osars in the same year since Lionel Richie in 1986.
          </p>










          <p>
            Other nominees for the category include <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/">Billie Eilish</a> and <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/finneas">Finneas</a>' <i>No Time to Die</i> <a target="_new" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BboMpayJomw&ab_channel=BillieEilishVEVO">theme</a>, <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/brian-wilson">Brian Wilson</a> and <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/jim-james">Jim James</a>' "<a target="_new" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_l5ynS5URCQ&ab_channel=BrianWilson">Right Where I Belong</a>," <a href="https://www.thefader.com/her">H.E.R.</a>'s "<a target="_new" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=et2CRPWAIkY&ab_channel=WarnerRecords">Automatic Woman</a>," and <a href="https://www.thefader.com/artist/u2">U2</a>'s "<a target="_new" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7KuGie4eWgQ&ab_channel=U2">Your Song Saved My Life</a>." Read the Academy's full shortlists for Best Original Score and Best Original Song below.
          </p>





      </div>


  </div>
</div>




      <div class="content_block paragraph triple_gutter_right triple_gutter_left">
        <div class="content_inner_wrapper">
          <div class="" style="padding-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: left;">
  <div class="ad  paragraph_wrapper">
    <div style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 5px;">ADVERTISEMENT</div>
        
<div id='div-above-latest-ad' >






      <div id="above-the-fold-ad">
        <script type='text/javascript'>
         var ad_id = displayAdSlot('above-the-fold-ad', 'fader_v3_article_above_the_fold3_300x250', [300, 250], true);
        </script>
      </div>





</div>


  </div>
</div>

        </div>
      </div>






    
<style>

</style>


  <div id="content_block-227575" class="content_block paragraph text triple_gutter_right triple_gutter_left center_align">
  <div class="content_inner_wrapper">


      <h5 class="headline" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
        Original Score
      </h5>


      <div class="paragraph_wrapper center_align">






          <p>
            Daniel Pemberton – <i>Being the Ricardos</i><br />Robert Aiki Aubrey Lowe – <i>Candyman</i><br />Nicholas Britell – <i>Don’t Look Up</i><br />Hans Zimmer – <i>Dune</i><br />Germaine Franco – <i>Encanto</i><br />Alexandre Desplat – <i>The French Dispatch of the Liberty, Kansas Evening Sun</i><br />Daniel Hart – <i>The Green Knight</i><br />Jeymes Samuel – <i>The Harder They Fall</i><br />Kris Bowers – <i>King Richard</i><br />Harry Gregson-Williams – <i>The Last Duel</i><br />Hans Zimmer – <i>No Time to Die</i><br />Alberto Iglesias – <i>Parallel Mothers</i><br />Jonny Greenwood – <i>The Power of the Dog</i><br />Jonny Greenwood – <i>Spencer</i><br />Carter Burwell – <i>The Tragedy of Macbeth</i>
          </p>





      </div>


  </div>
</div>










    
<style>

</style>


  <div id="content_block-227576" class="content_block paragraph text triple_gutter_right triple_gutter_left center_align">
  <div class="content_inner_wrapper">


      <h5 class="headline" style="margin-bottom: 30px;">
        Original Song
      </h5>


      <div class="paragraph_wrapper center_align">






          <p>
            Sparks, Adam Driver, and Marion Cotillard feat. Simon Hedberg – "So May We Start?" (<i>Annette</i>)<br />Van Morrison – "Down to Joy" (<i>Belfast</i>)<br />Brian Wilson & Jim James – "Right Where I Belong" (<i>Brian Wilson: Long Promised Road</i>)<br />H.E.R. – "Automatic Woman" (<i>Bruised</i>)<br />Cinderella Original Motion Picture Cast and Idina Menzel – "Dream Girl" (<i>Cinderella</i>)<br />Emilia Jones – "Beyond the Shore" (<i>Coda</i>)<br />Amandla Stenberg – "The Anonymous Ones" (<i>Dear Evan Hansen</i>)<br />Ariana Grande and Kid Cudi – "Just Look Up" (<i>Don’t Look Up</i>)<br />Sebastián Yatra – "Dos Oruguitas" (<i>Encanto</i>)<br />Reba McEntire – "Somehow You Do" (<i>Four Good Days</i>)<br />Jay-Z and Kid Cudi – "Guns Go Bang" (<i>The Harder They Fall</i>)<br />Beyoncé – "Be Alive" (<i>King Richard</i>)<br />Billie Eilish and Finneas – "No Time to Die" (<i>No Time to Die</i>)<br />Jennifer Hudson – "Here I Am (Singing My Way Home)" (<i>Respect</i>)<br />U2 – "Your Song Saved My Life" (<i>Sing 2</i>)
          </p>

            <div class="" style="padding-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 20px; text-align: left;">
  <div class="ad  paragraph_wrapper">
    <div style="color: #ccc; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 5px;">ADVERTISEMENT</div>
        
